WEBVTT

01:27.490 --> 01:31.920
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.100 --> 01:34.920
[Episode 1]

01:55.900 --> 01:56.910
[Li Hai University of Science and Technology]

01:56.940 --> 01:57.870
[2019 Professional Title Application Defense]

01:57.940 --> 02:00.660
[Yan Ling— Lecturer,
PhD in Marine Geography]

01:59.350 --> 02:00.760
My research focuses on

02:01.040 --> 02:03.120
the dynamics of storm surges
in shallow seas,

02:03.120 --> 02:05.280
as well as the prediction, forecasting,

02:05.280 --> 02:06.950
and risk assessment of marine disasters.

02:06.950 --> 02:09.729
[Li Hai University of Science and Technology]
[Published Books]

02:07.920 --> 02:10.250
These are the course hours I've completed

02:10.280 --> 02:12.500
and some of the projects I've worked on.

02:12.730 --> 02:15.630
[Published Journal Articles]

02:13.360 --> 02:16.070
Here are some of the papers I've published

02:16.190 --> 02:18.790
in major domestic
and international journals

02:18.870 --> 02:21.270
as first author and corresponding author.

02:24.060 --> 02:25.060
[Li Hai University of Science and Technology]

02:25.079 --> 02:26.030
[2019 Professional Title Application Defense]

02:25.840 --> 02:27.240
Your recent paper states that

02:26.090 --> 02:27.570
[Li Hai University of Science and Technology]
[Published Books]

02:27.240 --> 02:30.120
Professor Wang's
numerical forecasting product

02:30.640 --> 02:31.620
is outdated.

02:33.170 --> 02:34.570
That's not what I meant.

02:35.650 --> 02:38.990
[Published Journal Articles]

02:35.800 --> 02:38.260
I'm not trying to challenge
Professor Wang.

02:38.710 --> 02:41.240
It's just that the storm surge
overtopping coupling techniques

02:39.050 --> 02:42.740
[Li Hai University of Science and Technology]
[Published Books]

02:41.240 --> 02:43.079
have now become relatively mature.

02:43.079 --> 02:44.150
Professor Wang's previous research

02:44.150 --> 02:45.750
has been of great value to us,

02:45.870 --> 02:47.680
but the development of
artificial intelligence

02:47.680 --> 02:49.400
has indeed brought intelligent forecasting

02:49.400 --> 02:50.460
unprecedented...

02:51.960 --> 02:53.820
Stay back! I'll burn you to death!

02:59.520 --> 03:00.290
Get lost!

03:00.470 --> 03:01.360
Stay away!

03:02.910 --> 03:04.350
Don't push me!

03:04.520 --> 03:05.280
Go away!

03:05.430 --> 03:06.230
Li Changning?

03:07.840 --> 03:09.100
Ms. Yan, what's wrong?

03:10.400 --> 03:11.300
Changning!

03:15.080 --> 03:16.610
She's from our department.

03:16.960 --> 03:18.220
Don't come any closer!

03:18.310 --> 03:18.910
Calm down.

03:21.470 --> 03:22.170
Changning!

03:22.590 --> 03:23.150
Changning!

03:23.150 --> 03:24.320
Calm down!

03:26.520 --> 03:27.520
Get lost!

03:31.560 --> 03:32.310
Quick! Quick!

03:32.310 --> 03:34.190
Changning, what are you doing?

03:34.240 --> 03:35.910
Drop it! You'll burn yourself!

03:35.910 --> 03:38.000
Don't push me!

03:38.030 --> 03:38.690
Changning!

03:38.960 --> 03:40.310
Please calm down, okay?

03:40.710 --> 03:42.250
Drop it now!

03:42.560 --> 03:44.260
Changning!

03:44.470 --> 03:45.530
You'll get burned!

03:47.000 --> 03:48.360
Changning, calm down, alright?

03:48.360 --> 03:49.690
Tell me what happened.

03:49.750 --> 03:50.360
Okay?

03:51.680 --> 03:52.610
There's a demon.

03:52.730 --> 03:54.240
There's a demon following me.

03:54.240 --> 03:55.430
I'll burn you to death.

03:55.430 --> 03:56.760
I'll burn you to death!

03:57.800 --> 03:58.240
Right!

03:58.579 --> 03:59.380
I'm the demon!

04:00.190 --> 04:00.800
Burn me then!

04:00.800 --> 04:01.400
Come at me!

04:01.430 --> 04:02.130
Ms. Yan!

04:02.280 --> 04:02.680
Come on!

04:02.680 --> 04:03.280
Come at me!

04:03.470 --> 04:04.430
You don't dare?

04:05.800 --> 04:06.410
Come on!

04:08.500 --> 04:09.180
Changning!

04:12.430 --> 04:13.890
Quick! Call an ambulance!

04:28.870 --> 04:36.770
[Leilei]

04:36.840 --> 04:40.460
[Missed Call]

04:44.590 --> 04:48.090
[Emergency]

04:48.110 --> 04:50.180
[Emergency Exam Room] [Resuscitation Room]
[IV Infusion Room] [Wound Treatment Room]

04:51.070 --> 04:51.600
Yan Ling.

04:52.060 --> 04:52.770
How are you?

04:53.720 --> 04:54.450
You're hurt.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.880
It's nothing. Just a small wound.

04:55.880 --> 04:56.190
This is really...

04:56.190 --> 04:56.630
Please sit.

04:56.630 --> 04:57.159
Go on, you sit.

04:57.159 --> 04:57.600
Don't mind me.

04:57.600 --> 04:57.800
Here.

04:57.800 --> 04:58.330
Your bag.

04:58.480 --> 04:59.040
And your car keys.

04:59.040 --> 04:59.500
Thanks.

04:59.630 --> 05:00.030
Right.

05:00.200 --> 05:04.650
[Please Close the Door Behind You]
[Exhaust Fan Must Remain On]

05:00.310 --> 05:02.040
She just got a sedative shot
and hasn't woken up yet.

05:02.040 --> 05:05.000
They said a psychiatrist
will come for a consultation.

05:05.000 --> 05:06.310
Is she the girl

05:06.310 --> 05:08.110
whose thesis defense qualification
you canceled?

05:08.110 --> 05:08.560
Yes.

05:10.270 --> 05:11.630
Li Changning's family?

05:11.550 --> 05:12.320
[Please Close the Door Behind You]
[Exhaust Fan Must Remain On]

05:11.650 --> 05:12.380
Over here.

05:12.800 --> 05:13.530
Come with me.

05:17.480 --> 05:18.310
You two are?

05:18.830 --> 05:20.290
I'm her homeroom teacher.

05:20.290 --> 05:20.690
Right.

05:20.800 --> 05:21.360
And I'm

05:21.680 --> 05:23.210
the department secretary.

05:23.560 --> 05:24.180
Doctor,

05:24.390 --> 05:25.240
does this girl have

05:25.240 --> 05:26.700
some kind of mental issue?

05:26.950 --> 05:27.750
Is it serious?

05:28.750 --> 05:31.800
You said her thesis defense qualification
was canceled.

05:31.800 --> 05:33.930
That means she can't graduate, right?

05:34.510 --> 05:36.370
[Emergency Department
First-Contact Responsibility System]

05:35.360 --> 05:36.360
That's possible.

05:36.510 --> 05:38.040
So what is she usually like?

05:38.270 --> 05:40.490
Does she get along well with
her classmates and roommates?

05:40.490 --> 05:43.630
[Emergency Department
First-Contact Responsibility System]

05:42.830 --> 05:44.870
Let me explain something to you, doctor.

05:44.870 --> 05:46.510
Senior students are very busy.

05:46.510 --> 05:48.190
They need to look for jobs

05:48.190 --> 05:49.270
and prepare for graduate school exams.

05:49.270 --> 05:50.310
Their connection with the school side

05:50.310 --> 05:51.409
is quite loose.

05:51.950 --> 05:53.630
What about her family situation?

05:53.630 --> 05:55.430
Are there any emotional issues?

05:56.170 --> 05:59.120
[Emergency Department
First-Contact Responsibility System]

05:58.270 --> 05:59.070
I'm not sure.

06:01.160 --> 06:04.090
Is your homeroom teacher title
just an honorary one?

06:07.630 --> 06:09.430
Don't try to judge me.

06:09.870 --> 06:11.230
I don't need to prove

06:11.360 --> 06:13.240
what kind of teacher I am to anyone.

06:13.240 --> 06:14.480
I just want to know

06:14.600 --> 06:16.120
how my student is doing

06:16.190 --> 06:18.090
and what I can do to help her.

06:19.720 --> 06:21.160
Based on our preliminary examination,

06:21.160 --> 06:22.240
we can basically rule out

06:22.240 --> 06:22.770
alcohol,

06:22.950 --> 06:23.560
drugs,

06:23.680 --> 06:25.560
and certain psychiatric medications.

06:25.560 --> 06:26.950
She needs to stay for observation.

06:26.950 --> 06:29.880
Please notify her family to come
as soon as possible.

06:30.270 --> 06:31.160
Handle her hospital admission first.

06:31.160 --> 06:31.560
Okay.

06:31.560 --> 06:32.159
Thank you.

06:33.310 --> 06:33.909
Excuse me.

06:35.680 --> 06:37.070
Please stay for a moment.

06:37.070 --> 06:37.700
Me?

06:39.070 --> 06:40.240
It's actually nothing serious.

06:40.240 --> 06:41.430
I've rinsed it with cold water.

06:41.430 --> 06:42.270
Let me tell you.

06:42.270 --> 06:44.040
If this wound isn't treated properly

06:42.490 --> 06:44.270
[Disposal Room
Disinfection and Isolation Protocol]

06:44.040 --> 06:47.300
and gets infected, it could lead to
serious consequences.

06:48.040 --> 06:49.310
I'll go register then.

06:50.120 --> 06:51.510
Dr. Luo brought you here.

06:51.510 --> 06:52.720
There's no need to register.

06:52.720 --> 06:54.520
I can treat it for you right away.

06:54.950 --> 07:01.480
[Disposal Room
Disinfection and Isolation Protocol]

06:55.510 --> 06:56.310
Thank you.

06:57.950 --> 06:58.550
Ms. Zhang,

06:58.720 --> 06:59.630
you're so kind.

07:00.270 --> 07:01.750
Don't mention it, Dr. Luo.

07:11.070 --> 07:11.600
Yan Ling.

07:11.640 --> 07:14.030
[Pre-Triage]

07:13.000 --> 07:14.260
You've got it treated?

07:14.600 --> 07:15.430
That Dr. Luo

07:15.430 --> 07:16.800
is quite attentive.

07:17.750 --> 07:18.600
I forgot.

07:19.390 --> 07:20.800
You just had quite a scare.

07:20.800 --> 07:22.040
Of course you need a drink.

07:22.040 --> 07:23.570
Liquor-filled chocolate.

07:23.830 --> 07:24.270
Here.

07:24.690 --> 07:26.490
Don't let Jiale know about this.

07:29.580 --> 07:30.980
I forgot to pick up Jiale.

07:32.409 --> 07:34.100
[Calls]

07:34.200 --> 07:35.409
[Ms. Xu of Class 3, Grade 4]
[Hang up] [Answer]

07:35.730 --> 07:39.890
[Emergency]

07:39.480 --> 07:40.310
Ms. Xu.

07:41.040 --> 07:43.240
I'm sorry, I got caught up in something.

07:43.270 --> 07:44.480
How's Jiale...

07:47.000 --> 07:48.659
He was picked up by his father?

07:49.510 --> 07:50.440
Got it, alright.

07:50.510 --> 07:51.430
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

07:51.430 --> 07:52.240
Thank you.

07:56.440 --> 07:59.900
[Leilei]

07:57.560 --> 08:00.600
Hello, the number you dialed
is powered off.

08:00.950 --> 08:02.280
Please try again later.

08:04.750 --> 08:08.040
Hello, the number you dialed
is powered off.

08:08.060 --> 08:09.560
Please try again later.

08:17.630 --> 08:18.190
Coming.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.310
I'm sorry.

08:23.310 --> 08:24.440
I was caught up in...

08:25.360 --> 08:26.800
I was caught up in something
at school today.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.240
It's alright.

08:27.240 --> 08:28.050
Come on in.

08:28.240 --> 08:28.920
Why did I put it here?

08:28.920 --> 08:29.550
Pardon me.

08:38.990 --> 08:39.850
Where's Jiale?

08:40.169 --> 08:41.460
H-He fell asleep.

08:41.600 --> 08:43.360
What happened to your hand?

08:44.770 --> 08:46.770
I accidentally scraped it a little.

08:46.790 --> 08:47.840
Go get him for me.

08:47.840 --> 08:48.550
Let's not do that. It's so late.

08:48.550 --> 08:49.150
Just let him sleep here.

08:49.150 --> 08:50.320
I'll take him to school tomorrow.

08:50.320 --> 08:51.530
It's not the weekend.

08:51.630 --> 08:52.490
Just go get him.

08:59.980 --> 09:01.330
I'm sorry.

09:01.360 --> 09:03.090
I was late picking you up today.

09:03.720 --> 09:04.510
It's fine.

09:04.670 --> 09:06.470
It wasn't the first time anyway.

09:07.550 --> 09:08.510
Actually, you didn't have to
worry about me

09:08.510 --> 09:10.240
now that you wounded your hand.

09:10.390 --> 09:11.920
I could've stayed with Dad.

09:13.000 --> 09:14.130
Yeah... Better not.

09:14.670 --> 09:16.670
I saw a pair of slippers there today.

09:16.870 --> 09:17.800
So it might not be

09:18.120 --> 09:19.910
very convenient for you to visit him
from now on.

09:19.910 --> 09:21.240
You mean Miss Fang Fang?

09:22.480 --> 09:24.000
She won't mind.

09:24.390 --> 09:26.360
We actually get along pretty well.

09:28.030 --> 09:29.360
You've already met her?

09:29.810 --> 09:31.220
Why didn't you tell me?

09:32.920 --> 09:34.120
Why should I tell you?

09:35.670 --> 09:37.440
Didn't you tell me

09:37.960 --> 09:39.750
that you two are my parents,

09:39.910 --> 09:41.240
but not a couple?

09:46.030 --> 09:48.150
Oh right, what time
did Godmother and you agree on

09:48.150 --> 09:50.350
to pick me up tomorrow for the premiere?

09:51.220 --> 09:52.680
We haven't made plans yet.

09:52.710 --> 09:54.120
I couldn't reach her.

09:58.360 --> 10:01.200
Leilei, is your phone dead?

09:58.900 --> 10:00.890
[Release to Send]

10:01.200 --> 10:04.080
-Jiale has been asking about you...
-Let me talk to Godmother.

10:04.080 --> 10:04.600
Alright, you talk.

10:04.600 --> 10:05.260
Godmother.

10:05.320 --> 10:06.600
The premiere is tomorrow.

10:06.600 --> 10:08.160
Don't forget to pick me up.

10:22.390 --> 10:23.030
Is it done?

10:23.270 --> 10:23.840
Yes, it's done.

10:23.840 --> 10:24.630
Let's go eat.

10:24.630 --> 10:26.310
Sandwiches coming up.

10:32.550 --> 10:33.750
It's raining so hard.

10:34.040 --> 10:35.700
There will definitely be heavy traffic.

10:35.700 --> 10:37.240
We need to leave for school early.

10:37.240 --> 10:39.390
I'll wash the dishes after school today.

10:39.390 --> 10:40.590
Your hand is injured.

10:41.770 --> 10:43.230
That's thoughtful of you.

10:46.030 --> 10:46.630
By the way,

10:46.790 --> 10:47.750
after the movie tonight,

10:47.750 --> 10:49.630
don't ask Godmother
to take you for hot pot.

10:49.630 --> 10:50.890
She's on a diet lately.

10:51.060 --> 10:53.520
I know.
She needs to fit into a wedding dress.

10:55.270 --> 10:56.800
Did Godmother reply to you?

10:57.020 --> 10:57.900
Let me check.

10:59.480 --> 11:00.680
It must be Godmother.

11:01.450 --> 11:02.500
Unknown number.

11:05.510 --> 11:06.570
Hello, who's this?

11:06.670 --> 11:07.070
Hello,

11:07.150 --> 11:08.390
is this Yan Ling?

11:08.660 --> 11:09.460
Yeah, it's me.

11:09.790 --> 11:11.340
Do you know Jian Leilei?

11:14.780 --> 11:18.100
Hello, the number you dialed
is powered off.

11:18.170 --> 11:19.700
Please try again later.

11:21.120 --> 11:24.390
Hello, the number you dialed
is powered off.

11:24.510 --> 11:26.170
Please try again later.

11:47.670 --> 11:48.870
Do you recognize her?

11:56.750 --> 11:57.880
How could this be...

12:00.200 --> 12:01.360
How could this be...

12:16.560 --> 12:18.480
According to traffic surveillance footage,

12:18.480 --> 12:20.030
last night, the deceased herself

12:18.920 --> 12:22.070
[February 20, 2019]
[Longhui River]

12:20.200 --> 12:21.930
drove the car to the riverside.

13:13.780 --> 13:14.680
[February 20, 2019]
[Longhui River]

13:14.700 --> 13:17.120
[February 20, 2019]
[Longhui River]

13:19.390 --> 13:23.000
This is the footage captured by
cameras near Longhui River that night.

13:23.000 --> 13:24.500
Based on our on-site investigation,

13:24.500 --> 13:26.850
there're no other visible injuries
on the victim's body.

13:24.780 --> 13:30.410
[February 20, 2019]
[Longhui River]

13:27.360 --> 13:29.550
We suspect the deceased intentionally
used car exhaust

13:29.550 --> 13:32.030
to cause herself to suffer
carbon monoxide poisoning.

13:32.030 --> 13:33.200
The preliminary determination is

13:33.200 --> 13:33.770
suicide.

13:38.120 --> 13:40.000
Leilei couldn't have committed suicide.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.670
She couldn't have.

13:41.950 --> 13:44.690
She would never leave her parents behind.

13:45.480 --> 13:46.910
Besides, she was about to get married.

13:46.910 --> 13:47.310
She...

13:48.270 --> 13:49.480
Everything was going well for her.

13:49.480 --> 13:51.510
She had no reason to do this.

13:53.080 --> 13:53.720
Ms. Yan.

13:54.320 --> 13:56.480
You mentioned
she was about to get married?

13:56.480 --> 13:57.830
Who's her fiance?

14:01.600 --> 14:02.600
His name is Xia Yi.

14:03.840 --> 14:04.640
The two of them

14:05.670 --> 14:08.120
met at a bank reception.

14:09.900 --> 14:12.160
They've always had a good relationship.

14:13.840 --> 14:15.900
Do you have his contact information?

14:16.390 --> 14:17.440
No, I don't.

14:18.840 --> 14:20.640
Leilei must have it on her phone.

14:25.510 --> 14:26.030
Ms. Yan,

14:26.350 --> 14:28.390
[Dad, Mom. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.]

14:27.040 --> 14:28.100
please take a look.

14:28.510 --> 14:30.510
Is this Jian Leilei's handwriting?

14:34.390 --> 14:34.840
Dad,

14:36.840 --> 14:37.200
Mom.

14:39.630 --> 14:40.270
I'm sorry.

14:40.960 --> 14:42.270
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

14:44.910 --> 14:46.790
I've made a terrible mistake

14:48.550 --> 14:50.810
that I can't make up for in this lifetime.

14:51.240 --> 14:53.840
I owe you too much.

14:54.200 --> 14:55.930
I'll repay you in the next life.

14:57.200 --> 14:58.430
I'm sorry, Jiale.

14:58.630 --> 15:00.630
I can't be there to watch you grow up.

15:00.960 --> 15:02.240
I will always love you.

15:03.960 --> 15:04.910
I'm sorry, Ling.

15:05.960 --> 15:09.290
In our next life, I promise
we'll travel the world together.

15:09.750 --> 15:10.350
Remember,

15:11.080 --> 15:12.420
you must live well

15:12.750 --> 15:13.440
for me...

15:14.120 --> 15:15.440
For my sake.

15:16.200 --> 15:17.390
You promised me.

15:29.240 --> 15:29.600
Here.

15:34.030 --> 15:35.270
Where's our Leilei?

15:35.300 --> 15:37.000
-This way.
-Where's our Leilei?

15:37.000 --> 15:37.360
Come with me.

15:37.120 --> 15:43.300
[Police]

15:39.510 --> 15:40.570
Careful. Careful.

15:43.430 --> 15:46.380
[Emergency Department Lobby]
[Emergency Exam Room]

15:46.550 --> 15:47.430
Mrs. Feng.

15:47.910 --> 15:48.910
I have to trouble you again

15:48.910 --> 15:51.080
to go check on Li Changning for me today.

15:51.080 --> 15:53.030
I've got something urgent to handle

15:53.030 --> 15:54.100
and can't get away.

15:55.720 --> 15:56.920
It's not about my son.

15:56.960 --> 15:58.160
It's something else.

15:59.030 --> 16:02.400
[Emergency]

15:59.480 --> 16:00.510
Okay, I understand.

16:00.510 --> 16:01.110
Thank you.

16:09.790 --> 16:10.440
Uncle,

16:11.680 --> 16:12.810
how is Auntie doing?

16:13.520 --> 16:14.380
A bit better.

16:15.750 --> 16:16.430
Yan Ling,

16:17.440 --> 16:18.660
could you please

16:18.810 --> 16:20.270
take me to Leilei's place?

16:20.780 --> 16:22.760
I want to get a pair of shoes for her.

16:27.410 --> 16:28.270
No problem.

16:32.620 --> 16:33.420
Sorry.

16:33.840 --> 16:36.550
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

16:36.550 --> 16:37.900
Please try again later.

16:39.080 --> 16:40.480
Leilei mentioned before

16:41.510 --> 16:43.030
that when Xia Yi's on a mission,

16:43.030 --> 16:44.690
his phone often has no signal.

16:45.060 --> 16:46.200
Once he sees it,

16:46.360 --> 16:47.530
he will call back.

16:48.510 --> 16:50.110
She was doing so well.

16:51.630 --> 16:52.960
How could she suddenly

16:54.080 --> 16:55.440
lose hope like that?

17:16.490 --> 17:16.920
[To Ling]

17:16.920 --> 17:19.930
[Bank Card Number] [Password]
[WeChat Account] [Password]

17:19.950 --> 17:23.300
[Weibo Account] [Password]
[Alipay Account] [Password]

17:27.869 --> 17:30.080
[Personal Insurance Application Form]

17:41.860 --> 17:46.170
[Household Register]

17:48.000 --> 17:49.200
Why did you do this?

17:51.440 --> 17:53.440
Why did you do this...

17:57.310 --> 17:58.840
I'll go get some toiletries

17:58.880 --> 18:00.000
for you and Auntie.

18:34.130 --> 18:37.220
[Police]

18:35.280 --> 18:35.920
It's freezing outside.

18:35.920 --> 18:37.450
Wouldn't it be better to
enjoy some hotpot?

18:37.450 --> 18:38.200
You prefer to come here instead, huh?

18:38.040 --> 18:40.820
[Reception Area]

18:38.350 --> 18:39.080
Move faster!

18:39.480 --> 18:40.080
Chubby Li,

18:40.480 --> 18:41.550
help me take a statement.

18:41.550 --> 18:43.070
I don't have time, bro.

18:43.070 --> 18:44.400
I haven't even finished the briefing
for the higher-ups

18:44.400 --> 18:46.750
about that suicide case
I'm the liaison for.

18:46.750 --> 18:48.210
Look at all this fat on you.

18:48.400 --> 18:49.680
If you don't get more active,

18:49.680 --> 18:51.070
how will you pass the physical test?

18:51.070 --> 18:53.950
Master, I'm just office staff.
I don't need to go on patrol.

18:53.950 --> 18:55.310
Running into that suicide case yesterday

18:55.310 --> 18:56.290
was purely accidental.

18:55.900 --> 18:57.140
[General Services Window]

18:56.550 --> 18:57.080
Officer.

18:57.270 --> 18:57.790
Report!

18:58.160 --> 18:58.620
Report!

18:58.880 --> 18:59.790
We're here to file a report.

18:59.790 --> 19:00.590
We're here to file a report.

19:00.590 --> 19:01.070
Here's the thing.

19:01.070 --> 19:03.000
I'm from the Binjiang Branch
of Ninghai Commercial Bank,

19:03.000 --> 19:04.110
Jian Leilei's direct supervisor.

19:04.110 --> 19:04.960
My surname is Zhang.

19:04.960 --> 19:05.830
This afternoon,

19:05.830 --> 19:07.590
the police informed us
that something happened to Jian Leilei.

19:07.590 --> 19:08.050
Yes.

19:08.270 --> 19:09.270
She was our VIP client.

19:09.270 --> 19:10.310
Let me take it from here.

19:10.310 --> 19:11.440
That Jian Leilei

19:11.440 --> 19:13.270
had always been
my personal financial advisor.

19:13.270 --> 19:13.720
She had

19:13.720 --> 19:14.240
been managing

19:14.240 --> 19:15.880
some of my liquid funds here in China.

19:15.880 --> 19:17.480
I just returned from abroad.

19:17.590 --> 19:18.030
I had

19:18.030 --> 19:19.640
an appointment at the bank this morning

19:19.640 --> 19:21.160
with her and Manager Zhang

19:21.310 --> 19:23.390
to talk about a new financial plan,

19:23.590 --> 19:24.850
but she didn't show up.

19:26.160 --> 19:27.720
I checked my account, and it was shocking—

19:27.720 --> 19:28.920
she stole 1.8 million yuan

19:28.920 --> 19:30.780
from my account!

19:31.200 --> 19:31.800
That much?

19:56.110 --> 19:57.440
What's wrong, Yan Ling?

20:00.000 --> 20:00.860
Before, Leilei

20:01.400 --> 20:03.110
was worried you and Auntie
would be upset,

20:03.110 --> 20:04.910
so she probably didn't tell you.

20:06.110 --> 20:07.200
Actually, she and Xia Yi

20:07.200 --> 20:09.400
had been living together for some time.

20:09.720 --> 20:11.120
But now, there's no trace

20:11.720 --> 20:13.640
of Xia Yi's presence here at all.

20:21.160 --> 20:21.640
Master.

20:22.030 --> 20:24.160
We've obtained
Jian Leilei's bank statements

20:24.160 --> 20:26.030
and tracked the money trail in detail.

20:26.030 --> 20:27.640
We found that
starting about two months ago,

20:27.640 --> 20:29.830
she had been frequently
operating client accounts.

20:29.830 --> 20:31.550
At first, she would transfer money
to her own card

20:31.550 --> 20:32.880
and return it after a while.

20:32.880 --> 20:34.960
Later, money only went in
but never came out again.

20:34.960 --> 20:37.480
In total, she misappropriated about

20:38.070 --> 20:39.070
1.8 million yuan.

20:40.720 --> 20:42.550
She used it all
to buy a type of cryptocurrency.

20:42.550 --> 20:44.110
She even used triple leverage.

20:44.110 --> 20:45.040
Until recently,

20:45.190 --> 20:47.200
when this cryptocurrency
suddenly crashed in value,

20:47.200 --> 20:49.460
Jian Leilei basically lost everything.

20:50.830 --> 20:52.550
Suspected of misappropriating funds?

20:52.550 --> 20:53.210
And

20:53.720 --> 20:55.000
the amount is substantial.

20:55.000 --> 20:55.730
I had no idea.

20:56.030 --> 20:57.160
Absolutely no idea.

20:57.750 --> 20:58.480
Our Leilei

20:58.480 --> 21:00.410
had always been an honest girl.

21:00.510 --> 21:03.510
She couldn't possibly have done
something like this!

21:03.720 --> 21:04.850
That's impossible.

21:05.720 --> 21:07.650
Leilei wasn't that kind of person.

21:08.590 --> 21:10.790
We've obtained the relevant evidence.

21:13.070 --> 21:15.800
Did you family members
really not know anything?

21:16.750 --> 21:18.640
Jian Leilei's call records show

21:18.960 --> 21:20.420
that for over a month,

21:20.590 --> 21:22.920
she hasn't been in contact
with this Xia Yi

21:23.200 --> 21:24.200
that you mentioned.

21:24.200 --> 21:25.920
No contact for over a month?

21:27.200 --> 21:30.200
None of the phone numbers
in Jian Leilei's call records

21:30.200 --> 21:32.110
belong to anyone named Xia Yi.

21:33.030 --> 21:33.680
Besides,

21:34.400 --> 21:36.000
in the trunk of Jian Leilei's car,

21:36.000 --> 21:37.930
we found a box full of luxury goods—

21:38.920 --> 21:39.980
roughly estimated

21:40.400 --> 21:42.240
to be worth nearly a million yuan.

21:42.240 --> 21:44.700
Only her fingerprints
were found on the box.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.110
Do you

21:47.960 --> 21:49.480
really know Jian Leilei?

21:53.140 --> 21:55.700
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

21:59.320 --> 22:00.490
Jian, still working?

21:59.700 --> 22:01.260
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

22:00.790 --> 22:01.560
I was about to leave.

22:01.560 --> 22:05.070
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

22:02.000 --> 22:02.600
Oh, right.

22:02.680 --> 22:03.790
Tomorrow at 10 AM,

22:03.810 --> 22:06.210
don't forget the meeting with that client.

22:06.270 --> 22:07.640
Okay, don't worry.

22:24.840 --> 22:32.680
[Leilei]

22:32.790 --> 22:36.040
[Missed Call]

22:37.960 --> 22:38.680
Why?

22:40.590 --> 22:42.750
Why did I miss your call?

22:43.500 --> 22:46.040
[Calls]

22:46.310 --> 22:48.070
Why did I fail to save you?

22:52.320 --> 22:52.880
Leilei.

22:56.510 --> 22:57.400
You're gone.

23:00.310 --> 23:01.640
What am I supposed to do?

23:15.770 --> 23:18.570
[Radiotherapy Department]

23:17.930 --> 23:19.590
Folks, who can relate?

23:19.590 --> 23:21.640
A college professor has turned into
a demon to torture her student.

23:21.640 --> 23:22.830
Come at me!

23:22.830 --> 23:23.640
I'm the demon!

23:23.640 --> 23:24.310
Come at me!

23:24.310 --> 23:25.590
Bring it on!

23:25.590 --> 23:26.240
I'm the demon!

23:26.240 --> 23:26.840
Come at me!

23:30.980 --> 23:31.750
Do you think it was easy for us

23:31.750 --> 23:34.880
to work ourselves to death
to support a college student?

23:34.960 --> 23:36.290
Now you won't let her graduate,

23:36.290 --> 23:37.240
and you've even driven her crazy.

23:37.240 --> 23:38.920
Are you trying to shirk responsibility?

23:38.920 --> 23:39.810
I admit that

23:39.880 --> 23:42.470
I didn't pay enough attention
to Li Changning's mental health.

23:42.470 --> 23:43.960
But her graduation thesis

23:44.270 --> 23:46.550
has a plagiarism rate of 40%.

23:46.750 --> 23:48.920
If I had given her
the thesis defense qualification,

23:48.920 --> 23:49.880
it would have been unfair

23:49.880 --> 23:51.750
to the students

23:51.790 --> 23:52.720
who worked seriously on their theses.

23:52.720 --> 23:55.440
I don't understand what you're
talking about, plague rate or something.

23:55.440 --> 23:56.310
You drove her crazy.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.510
You have to take responsibility for that!

23:57.510 --> 23:58.160
Calm down.

23:58.160 --> 24:00.240
Let's talk things out properly, alright?

24:00.240 --> 24:01.920
If we just give her a diploma like this,

24:01.920 --> 24:03.780
I believe when she recovers,

24:03.960 --> 24:05.760
she'll feel ashamed of herself.

24:05.880 --> 24:07.960
What if she faces problems again
in the future?

24:07.960 --> 24:11.070
Will there always be someone
protecting her and giving in to her?

24:11.070 --> 24:12.670
How could you hit her?

24:12.750 --> 24:13.920
-What are you doing?
-We could talk things out.

24:13.920 --> 24:14.270
How could you resort to violence?

24:14.270 --> 24:15.330
This is a hospital,

24:15.400 --> 24:16.880
not a place for violence and aggression!

24:16.880 --> 24:17.720
Call security!

24:17.720 --> 24:18.440
Calm down.

24:18.440 --> 24:20.720
-Look what happened to our daughter...
-Calm down.

24:20.720 --> 24:21.380
Pay up!

24:21.410 --> 24:22.470
Compensate me now!

24:23.090 --> 24:23.550
Ms. Yan.

24:23.550 --> 24:24.790
You drove her crazy.

24:24.790 --> 24:25.590
You have to pay with your life!

24:25.590 --> 24:26.450
That's enough!

24:26.480 --> 24:27.360
Let's go.

24:27.790 --> 24:28.910
Look at my child!

24:28.960 --> 24:30.090
Don't use violence.

24:30.510 --> 24:31.110
Pay up now!

24:31.880 --> 24:32.470
Director Lin.

24:32.470 --> 24:33.400
Regarding the diploma,

24:33.400 --> 24:34.070
you need to resolve it for us.

24:34.070 --> 24:35.130
Listen to me, okay?

24:51.560 --> 24:52.490
Are you alright?

24:53.050 --> 24:53.660
I'm okay.

24:59.420 --> 25:00.070
Thank you.

25:07.440 --> 25:08.440
Put some ice on it.

25:08.590 --> 25:09.790
Your face is swollen.

25:10.080 --> 25:11.150
No need. Thank you.

25:11.350 --> 25:13.010
I specially bought it for you.

25:14.240 --> 25:15.500
Can you give me my keys?

25:15.640 --> 25:17.650
Your emotional state
isn't suitable for driving.

25:17.650 --> 25:18.450
It's not safe.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.500
Where are you going?

25:19.500 --> 25:20.270
If it's on the way,

25:20.270 --> 25:20.920
since I just got off work,

25:20.920 --> 25:21.960
I can give you a ride.

25:21.960 --> 25:22.550
I don't want to trouble you.

25:22.550 --> 25:23.430
I can manage.

25:23.570 --> 25:24.370
No, you can't.

25:26.510 --> 25:27.640
It's too dangerous.

25:28.290 --> 25:30.150
This ear might have been injured.

25:30.440 --> 25:32.900
It could affect your balance
while driving.

25:33.370 --> 25:34.910
Even if you don't consider yourself,

25:34.910 --> 25:37.510
you should think about
innocent pedestrians.

25:41.110 --> 25:42.240
Where are you going?

25:44.440 --> 25:46.840
To the seafood restaurant on Shunbai Road.

25:51.030 --> 25:52.030
It's not on my way.

25:53.440 --> 25:55.480
But I've called a designated driver
for you.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.030
Thanks.

25:59.790 --> 26:00.680
I appreciate that,

26:00.680 --> 26:02.030
but I think adding you on WeChat is...

26:02.030 --> 26:03.160
You'll have to pay me

26:03.920 --> 26:05.180
for the driver, right?

26:07.860 --> 26:08.840
I'm sorry.

26:10.000 --> 26:10.780
I'm sorry.

26:24.350 --> 26:24.960
Ling.

26:27.240 --> 26:28.440
Isn't this restaurant expensive?

26:28.440 --> 26:29.790
This is Xia Yi's friend's restaurant.

26:29.790 --> 26:31.150
The decor looks so nice.

26:31.880 --> 26:33.070
Getting married?

26:33.350 --> 26:35.590
You've only known each other
for a few months.

26:35.590 --> 26:36.920
Isn't that a bit too fast?

26:36.920 --> 26:37.920
It's not.

26:37.920 --> 26:39.740
I know he's the one.

26:40.400 --> 26:41.590
How should I explain that feeling to you?

26:41.590 --> 26:42.790
He just gets me,

26:42.790 --> 26:45.400
and he genuinely appreciates me
from the bottom of his heart.

26:45.400 --> 26:47.590
Ms. Yan, I've finally met you.

26:47.920 --> 26:49.920
Leilei talks about you all the time.

26:49.960 --> 26:51.030
You're her idol.

26:51.960 --> 26:54.260
He's a maritime rescue volunteer.

26:54.350 --> 26:56.680
The first time we met,
he took me to the fish market.

26:56.680 --> 26:59.310
We saw a type of crab there.

26:59.310 --> 27:00.590
It looked like a flower crab,

27:00.590 --> 27:01.590
but it was actually highly poisonous.

27:01.590 --> 27:02.920
Eating it would land you
in intensive care.

27:02.920 --> 27:03.680
Xia Yi said

27:03.680 --> 27:05.680
this crab has a scientific name called...

27:05.680 --> 27:06.740
What's that again?

27:06.920 --> 27:08.200
Devil crab.

27:08.310 --> 27:10.370
Even more poisonous than jellyfish.

27:12.110 --> 27:12.590
Miss.

27:13.750 --> 27:15.640
Was something wrong with your meal?

27:15.640 --> 27:16.200
No.

27:16.470 --> 27:18.070
I'm here to look for someone.

27:19.000 --> 27:21.000
He often dines here,

27:21.020 --> 27:22.440
and he says he's a friend of yours.

27:22.440 --> 27:27.580
[Reservation: October 14—Ms. Jian]

27:23.200 --> 27:24.530
You mean Mr. Xia, right?

27:25.030 --> 27:26.400
He's a regular customer here,

27:26.400 --> 27:28.110
but he hasn't come here for a while.

27:27.600 --> 27:28.990
[Reservation: October 12—Ms. Jian]

27:29.510 --> 27:32.170
It was always Leilei
who made the reservations.

27:32.310 --> 27:33.550
Waiter, check please.

27:33.550 --> 27:34.160
Certainly.

27:34.160 --> 27:35.400
Sir, did you drive here?

27:35.400 --> 27:36.920
If we register your license plate,

27:36.920 --> 27:38.110
you can enjoy free parking.

27:38.110 --> 27:39.060
No need, thank you.

27:39.060 --> 27:39.440
Okay.

27:40.440 --> 27:41.000
Ms. Yan.

27:42.270 --> 27:43.470
I've finally met you.

27:43.490 --> 27:44.110
Sir.

27:44.790 --> 27:46.880
Could you please check the parking records

27:45.540 --> 27:47.420
[Reservation: October 18—Ms. Jian]

27:46.880 --> 27:49.280
for Miss Jian and her party
on October 18th?

27:49.550 --> 27:49.920
Sure.

27:49.920 --> 27:50.720
Just a moment.

27:51.640 --> 27:52.070
Hello,

27:52.070 --> 27:53.000
is this 114?

27:54.590 --> 27:56.590
Could you help me contact

27:56.590 --> 27:59.390
the owner of the car with license plate
Dong A 4728K

27:59.790 --> 28:02.160
and ask them to move their car
as soon as possible?

28:02.160 --> 28:02.560
No, no.

28:02.790 --> 28:03.750
It's like this.

28:04.070 --> 28:06.240
I accidentally scratched their car.

28:06.600 --> 28:08.350
I need to contact them directly

28:08.350 --> 28:10.680
to see how we should handle the insurance.

28:20.830 --> 28:21.480
Xia Yi.

28:26.400 --> 28:27.400
Car rental?

28:32.920 --> 28:34.430
Godmother, push me.

28:34.680 --> 28:35.950
Higher, Godmother.

28:36.110 --> 28:37.270
A little higher.

28:40.240 --> 28:40.980
Higher...

28:41.750 --> 28:42.820
[Sometimes kids' fun is really simple.]

28:51.050 --> 28:53.130
[My son says his godmother's
beef pies are the best in the world.]

28:56.420 --> 28:57.390
[You're a year older. In the new year,]

28:57.410 --> 28:58.790
[let's level up
and fight the monsters together.]

29:02.370 --> 29:02.600
[Godmother's exact words: "If you see the bear,
it's like seeing me—if the bear's here, I'm here."]

29:02.630 --> 29:03.040
[She really doesn't mind
how small our living room is.]

29:03.070 --> 29:05.420
["Memories" Music Festival]

29:05.440 --> 29:06.360
[has been accompanying Leilei and me for
countless days and nights.]

29:06.380 --> 29:07.350
[We're finally going to hear it live.]

29:07.380 --> 29:08.390
[Tonight, let's stay up
all night together.]

29:16.480 --> 29:18.800
♪ It's like a dream ♪

29:19.680 --> 29:22.620
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

29:23.890 --> 29:25.320
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

29:25.600 --> 29:30.130
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

29:31.450 --> 29:37.930
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

29:38.910 --> 29:44.460
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

29:42.210 --> 29:46.210
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

29:49.960 --> 29:51.410
Bed 23, Li Changning.

29:58.000 --> 29:59.860
Here, take this before you sleep.

30:27.640 --> 30:30.590
Changning used to live in the dormitory.

30:30.640 --> 30:33.570
She only moved out
at the beginning of this semester.

30:33.960 --> 30:34.920
Moved out?

30:35.960 --> 30:37.200
Does she live alone?

30:40.280 --> 30:42.680
The rent near the school
isn't cheap, is it?

30:44.720 --> 30:46.160
W-We're not really sure.

30:46.580 --> 30:48.370
She doesn't seem short of money.

30:48.370 --> 30:50.300
She bought the latest phone model,

30:50.510 --> 30:52.840
saying it was a birthday gift
for a friend.

30:53.480 --> 30:54.160
A friend?

30:55.160 --> 30:56.030
Her boyfriend?

30:57.490 --> 30:58.400
No idea.

31:02.030 --> 31:02.480
Hello?

31:02.680 --> 31:03.260
Uncle.

31:09.240 --> 31:10.100
Please come in.

31:15.790 --> 31:16.270
Ms. Yan.

31:21.960 --> 31:24.690
I was on an island in Minzhou

31:25.270 --> 31:28.320
attending a closed
marine search and rescue training camp.

31:28.320 --> 31:29.120
I only saw

31:29.830 --> 31:30.890
the dozens of calls

31:31.410 --> 31:32.350
Uncle and the police made to me

31:32.350 --> 31:33.750
after I got back.

31:36.480 --> 31:37.740
What exactly happened

31:38.680 --> 31:40.010
between you and Leilei?

31:42.880 --> 31:43.920
About a month ago,

31:45.750 --> 31:47.030
we had a big fight.

31:47.820 --> 31:49.280
You want another 500,000?

31:50.560 --> 31:53.160
If it's not convenient,
less would be fine too.

31:53.480 --> 31:55.880
It's that cryptocurrency again, isn't it?

31:55.880 --> 31:58.140
We've already lost a lot of money on that.

31:58.640 --> 32:00.680
We can't keep pouring money
into it endlessly.

32:00.680 --> 32:01.480
You mean

32:02.270 --> 32:05.530
Leilei had already borrowed money
from you several times?

32:06.880 --> 32:07.480
Yes.

32:08.880 --> 32:10.160
Just now, Xia

32:10.720 --> 32:11.690
showed me

32:12.030 --> 32:13.830
his transfer records to Leilei.

32:13.830 --> 32:15.240
It started with 10,000 or 20,000,

32:15.240 --> 32:16.910
but then it kept increasing,

32:17.240 --> 32:20.070
to 50,000, 80,000, and even 100,000.

32:21.480 --> 32:23.480
Your family runs a big business.

32:23.480 --> 32:24.680
The little money I make

32:24.680 --> 32:26.240
certainly isn't impressive to you,

32:26.240 --> 32:28.140
but you don't have to look down on me,
right?

32:28.140 --> 32:29.000
How could you think that?

32:29.000 --> 32:31.660
It's your attitude
that makes me think this way.

32:31.920 --> 32:32.680
Xia Yi.

32:32.680 --> 32:34.960
I, Jian Leilei, don't depend on any man.

32:35.000 --> 32:36.480
If you think I'm only after your money,

32:36.480 --> 32:38.010
get out of my life right now!

32:38.880 --> 32:39.680
Leilei and I

32:40.480 --> 32:41.940
were about to get married.

32:42.070 --> 32:43.230
Actually, for me,

32:43.440 --> 32:45.300
it really wasn't about the money.

32:46.680 --> 32:48.480
The main problem was that Leilei

32:48.880 --> 32:50.310
had really gone too far.

32:51.240 --> 32:53.830
I originally thought
that while I was away,

32:54.110 --> 32:55.270
we could separate temporarily

32:55.270 --> 32:56.680
and both cool down a bit.

32:56.740 --> 32:57.510
If I had known
things would end up like this,

32:57.510 --> 32:59.570
I should have just lent her the money.

32:59.880 --> 33:00.620
Xia.

33:01.640 --> 33:03.920
As for the money
you transferred to Leilei,

33:03.920 --> 33:06.520
my wife and I will definitely
pay you back.

33:06.620 --> 33:07.350
No, Uncle,

33:08.270 --> 33:09.600
that's not what I meant.

33:10.660 --> 33:12.340
When Leilei was with you,

33:13.030 --> 33:14.690
did she ever use luxury goods?

33:15.350 --> 33:16.080
Yes, she did.

33:16.680 --> 33:18.750
Then why have I never seen them?

33:21.480 --> 33:23.400
Maybe she didn't want you to know.

33:25.590 --> 33:26.400
Do you

33:27.200 --> 33:28.880
really know Jian Leilei?

33:31.480 --> 33:31.880
Uncle.

33:33.200 --> 33:35.680
I hope you and Auntie
can take care of yourselves.

33:35.680 --> 33:36.680
My condolences.

33:39.310 --> 33:40.510
If you need anything,

33:41.070 --> 33:42.270
call me anytime.

33:45.750 --> 33:46.350
Thank you.

33:47.440 --> 33:48.040
Thank you.

33:50.570 --> 33:52.210
I need to get back to the hospital.

33:52.210 --> 33:53.540
My wife will be worried.

33:59.310 --> 34:01.110
Ms. Yan, I'll be going now too.

34:02.510 --> 34:03.030
Xia Yi.

34:05.880 --> 34:07.210
Can we talk for a moment?

34:10.630 --> 34:12.159
Why isn't your phone number

34:12.550 --> 34:13.760
under your name?

34:14.230 --> 34:15.960
Uncle just asked me about that.

34:16.590 --> 34:19.190
Our company set up a corporate plan
for all employees.

34:19.190 --> 34:21.190
The accountant gave me this SIM card,

34:21.190 --> 34:23.050
and I've been using it ever since.

34:23.710 --> 34:25.040
And what about your car?

34:25.440 --> 34:27.639
For business convenience, our company

34:27.760 --> 34:28.400
rented a Range Rover SUV

34:28.400 --> 34:30.110
for me here.

34:30.590 --> 34:32.250
Leilei loved driving around.

34:33.000 --> 34:33.840
You know that.

34:35.150 --> 34:37.150
Actually, I've already explained all this

34:37.150 --> 34:38.940
to Officer Li.

34:40.760 --> 34:41.400
Is that so?

34:49.699 --> 34:50.760
Hello, Officer Li.

34:51.400 --> 34:52.280
This is Xia Yi.

34:54.110 --> 34:54.570
Yes.

34:55.190 --> 34:57.120
I've already met Leilei's family.

34:58.400 --> 35:00.000
I've explained everything.

35:02.290 --> 35:04.420
Okay, thank you, Officer Li. Goodbye.

35:08.110 --> 35:08.630
Ms. Yan.

35:09.800 --> 35:10.930
I know you're upset.

35:11.550 --> 35:12.840
If you feel that

35:13.190 --> 35:14.070
yelling at me

35:14.070 --> 35:15.600
would make you feel better,

35:16.840 --> 35:17.760
I can take it.

35:18.800 --> 35:21.460
It might make me
feel a little better myself too.

35:39.140 --> 35:41.850
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

35:44.480 --> 35:46.190
This patient has developed
some drug resistance.

35:46.190 --> 35:47.520
We might need to do MECT.

35:47.630 --> 35:49.800
But his family
is quite resistant to electrotherapy.

35:49.800 --> 35:51.400
It's okay. I'll talk to them.

35:51.630 --> 35:53.000
Help me remind the attending physician

35:53.000 --> 35:54.710
to reduce the Chlorpromazine dosage.

35:54.710 --> 35:56.920
It does affect the cardiovascular system
to some extent.

35:56.920 --> 35:57.280
Okay.

36:16.950 --> 36:18.000
[Lihai University of Finance and Economics]

36:20.360 --> 36:20.930
Feng.

36:21.070 --> 36:21.750
Feng.

36:22.920 --> 36:23.590
Where's Feng?

36:23.590 --> 36:24.550
Do you know where Feng is?

36:24.550 --> 36:25.000
Where's Feng?

36:25.000 --> 36:25.730
I don't know.

36:27.550 --> 36:28.800
Do you know where Feng is?

36:28.800 --> 36:29.440
Where's Feng?

36:29.440 --> 36:32.840
-What Feng? From which department?
-Why ask if you don't know him?

36:32.840 --> 36:33.740
Are you crazy?

36:34.190 --> 36:34.950
Feng.

36:48.600 --> 36:50.600
I can die for you too!

36:50.630 --> 36:51.510
Feng!

36:52.140 --> 36:54.570
I can die for you too!

36:58.070 --> 36:59.400
I'm sorry, Teacher.

36:58.130 --> 37:01.430
[Lihai Renxin Hospital
Medical Case Records]

36:59.630 --> 37:01.190
I came to visit Changning today,

37:01.190 --> 37:02.230
and she kept begging me,

37:02.230 --> 37:02.760
saying

37:02.880 --> 37:04.360
she'd just go out for a while.

37:04.360 --> 37:06.890
And she said
there was nothing wrong with her.

37:06.920 --> 37:09.840
She was just pretending
to get her diploma

37:09.840 --> 37:11.040
and scare the school.

37:13.230 --> 37:15.200
Who is this "Feng" guy anyway?

37:16.360 --> 37:18.170
He's Changning's boyfriend.

37:18.280 --> 37:19.450
His name is Xu Feng.

37:19.880 --> 37:22.320
He's from
the University of Finance and Economics.

37:22.320 --> 37:23.510
But it seems

37:23.510 --> 37:26.170
they've been talking about
breaking up lately.

37:26.800 --> 37:29.110
You didn't report such a serious matter
to the school?

37:29.110 --> 37:30.360
Do you think you're helping her?

37:30.360 --> 37:31.590
You're hurting her.

37:32.510 --> 37:35.070
I've always told you
there's no use in girls getting educated.

37:35.070 --> 37:36.800
Now she's fooling around with some boy

37:36.800 --> 37:38.460
and making herself act crazy.

37:38.920 --> 37:39.590
How embarrassing!

37:39.590 --> 37:40.150
Keep it down.

37:40.150 --> 37:41.810
Take your hands off me! Let go!

37:45.760 --> 37:46.690
What's going on?

37:48.070 --> 37:48.730
Yan Ling,

37:48.920 --> 37:50.320
your name's been cleared.

37:50.320 --> 37:50.920
Li Changning

37:50.920 --> 37:52.050
is completely fine.

37:53.670 --> 37:56.070
Dr. Luo, what's going on with
Li Changning?

37:56.360 --> 37:58.050
She's in an acute stress state right now.

37:58.050 --> 37:59.980
We can't fully trust what she says.

38:00.150 --> 38:01.410
Excuse me, let me through.

38:01.410 --> 38:02.240
Dr. Luo,

38:02.920 --> 38:03.920
let me take a look.

38:03.960 --> 38:05.190
How are you injured so badly?

38:05.190 --> 38:05.840
There's no need for this.

38:05.840 --> 38:06.440
Tian Tian,

38:07.030 --> 38:08.630
please step outside for now.

38:13.510 --> 38:15.310
Based on the latest assessment,

38:15.360 --> 38:16.550
the real source of stress

38:16.550 --> 38:18.670
comes from Li Changning's
emotional relationships.

38:18.670 --> 38:20.130
Not being able to graduate

38:20.320 --> 38:22.580
was at most the last straw that broke her.

38:26.440 --> 38:28.550
You should at least
apologize to Ms. Yan.

38:28.550 --> 38:29.360
Changning's father,

38:29.360 --> 38:31.760
we could hold you responsible for assault.

38:32.430 --> 38:33.490
No need, it's okay.

38:36.360 --> 38:37.360
I have a child too.

38:38.240 --> 38:40.480
I understand how you felt at that moment.

38:40.480 --> 38:42.880
I'm sorry.

38:43.110 --> 38:45.920
She was actually a very obedient child
when she was little.

38:45.920 --> 38:47.070
Who'd have expected...

38:47.070 --> 38:49.440
Who'd have expected
that she would lie to us?

38:49.440 --> 38:50.900
The most urgent matter now

38:51.550 --> 38:53.510
is to get Changning proper treatment.

38:53.510 --> 38:55.910
As long as
she takes her studies seriously,

38:56.070 --> 38:57.130
once she recovers,

38:59.030 --> 39:01.690
I'll help her apply for
a graduation extension.

39:03.000 --> 39:05.060
Helping Changning go on with her life

39:05.070 --> 39:06.880
is more important than anything else.

39:06.880 --> 39:08.670
Thank you, Ms. Yan. Thank you.

39:20.510 --> 39:21.190
Yan Ling.

39:21.920 --> 39:24.260
The police said
the case is already closed.

39:24.260 --> 39:25.520
We can go pick up Leilei

39:25.590 --> 39:26.880
tomorrow.

39:27.440 --> 39:27.960
They said

39:27.960 --> 39:30.220
that even if there's a criminal suspect,

39:30.630 --> 39:32.300
according to national law,

39:32.800 --> 39:34.880
no criminal responsibility is pursued

39:34.880 --> 39:36.880
if the suspect is already deceased.

39:40.030 --> 39:40.940
I've decided—

39:41.000 --> 39:42.590
I'll choose tulips for my bouquet.

39:42.590 --> 39:43.900
Make sure you catch it.

40:16.970 --> 40:21.550
[Morgue]

40:25.300 --> 40:26.960
You can give the clothes to me.

40:31.150 --> 40:32.510
Our Leilei...

40:33.630 --> 40:34.590
Our Leilei

40:34.590 --> 40:37.360
died unmarried.

40:37.960 --> 40:38.790
Let me

40:39.550 --> 40:41.000
change her clothes.

40:43.670 --> 40:44.110
I...

40:44.110 --> 40:46.400
With your health condition,
I don't think it's a good idea.

40:46.400 --> 40:47.630
Given how emotional you are,

40:47.630 --> 40:48.970
if something happens,

40:49.070 --> 40:51.600
we won't be able to
take that responsibility.

40:54.980 --> 40:55.630
Auntie.

40:56.630 --> 40:57.630
Let me handle this.

40:57.630 --> 40:59.550
I'll go. Don't worry.

41:09.960 --> 41:10.490
This way.

41:14.470 --> 41:15.430
[Morgue]

41:16.440 --> 41:18.150
I want to see her one more time!

41:18.510 --> 41:28.390
I want to see my daughter one more time!

43:22.050 --> 43:25.720
[The Dark Romance]

43:57.230 --> 43:58.000
Bed 32.

43:58.000 --> 43:58.670
Tomorrow morning,

43:58.670 --> 44:00.320
schedule a neurosurgery consultation
for him.

44:00.320 --> 44:01.580
Make a note of it for me.

44:12.640 --> 44:13.360
Keep an eye on her!

44:13.360 --> 44:14.590
Li Changning, calm down!
